"Editor de imagini nativ macOS, model nedistructiv (XMP)." = "Native macOS image editor, non-destructive (XMP) model.";
"Ce este Photo2Mac" = "What is Photo2Mac";
"Photo2Mac este un editor de imagini nativ macOS, simplu si rapid. Modelul de editare este nedistructiv: pixelii originali nu se modifica decat la salvare; pana atunci, fiecare ajustare (decupare, rotire, flip, luminozitate, contrast, saturatie, expunere) e doar o instructiune in stiva de editari, randata live prin Core Image." = "Photo2Mac is a small, fast native macOS image editor. It's non-destructive: original pixels stay untouched until you save; until then, every adjustment (crop, rotate, flip, brightness, contrast, saturation, exposure) is just an instruction on the edit stack, rendered live through Core Image.";
"Stiva de editari se salveaza in metadata XMP a fisierului — deschiderea aceluiasi fisier in Photo2Mac restaureaza editarile (le poti modifica). Alte aplicatii vad doar pixelii randati." = "The edit stack is saved into the file's XMP metadata — reopening the same file in Photo2Mac restores the edits (you can keep tweaking). Other apps just see the rendered pixels.";
"Cum incepi" = "Getting started";
"File → Open image... (Cmd+O), drag-and-drop pe fereastra, sau alege o imagine recenta din ecranul de pornire." = "File → Open image… (Cmd+O), drag-and-drop on the window, or pick a recent image from the welcome screen.";
"Imaginile deschise apar ca tab-uri in partea de sus. Cmd+W inchide tab-ul curent, Cmd+Shift+W inchide fereastra (app-ul ramane viu)." = "Open images appear as tabs at the top. Cmd+W closes the current tab; Cmd+Shift+W closes the window (the app stays running).";
"Tool-uri" = "Tools";
"Mutare: mut imaginea in workspace (click-drag sau scroll trackpad)." = "Move: pans the image within the workspace (click-drag or trackpad scroll).";
"Decupare: dreptunghi de selectie cu colt-handles + edge-handles. Picker pentru raport (Original, 1:1, 4:3, ..., Liber). Apply commit-uieste." = "Crop: selection rectangle with corner + edge handles. Aspect ratio picker (Original, 1:1, 4:3, ..., Free). Apply commits.";
"Rotire: presets ±90°, slider 0.01° + text field pentru unghi precis, Flip H/V." = "Rotate: ±90° presets, 0.01° slider + text field for precise angle, Flip H/V.";
"Ajustari: histograma live (Luminanta/RGB/R/G/B) + sliders pentru Luminozitate, Contrast, Saturatie, Expunere." = "Adjustments: live histogram (Luminance/RGB/R/G/B) + Brightness, Contrast, Saturation, Exposure sliders.";
"Metadate: vezi EXIF (camera, ISO, expunere, etc.) si statusul XMP-ului Photo2Mac (JSON brut optional)." = "Metadata: shows EXIF (camera, ISO, shutter, etc.) and the Photo2Mac XMP status (raw JSON optional).";
"Save / persistare" = "Saving / persistence";
"Cmd+S scrie peste fisierul deschis: pixeli randati + stack EditStack ca XMP. macOS retine si o versiune anterioara prin NSFileVersion." = "Cmd+S overwrites the open file: rendered pixels + EditStack as XMP. macOS keeps a previous version via NSFileVersion.";
"Cmd+Shift+S = Save As cu panel." = "Cmd+Shift+S = Save As with a panel.";
"Daca inchizi tab-ul fara save, editarile se pastreaza intr-un autosave invisible (App Support); la reopen primesti prompt pentru a continua sau renunta." = "Close a tab without saving and your edits live on as an invisible autosave (App Support); reopening prompts to continue or discard.";
